Source: dfm-tools-plugins
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: zhanghongyuan <zhanghongyuan@uniontech.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://gitee.com/sunstom/dfm-tools.git

Package: dfm-tools-plugins
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
  dfm-tools-integration-all,
  dfm-tools-gitk,
  dfm-tools-git-cola,
  dfm-tools-deb-builder,
  dfm-tools-deepin-project-downloader,
  dfm-tools-dde-dconfig-editor,
  dfm-tools-changelog-update,
  dfm-tools-d-feet,
  dfm-tools-vscode,
  dfm-tools-qtcreator,
  dfm-tools-deb-saver
Description: Meta package for DDE File Manager extra context menu plugins
 This is a meta package that depends on all individual context menu plugins
 for Deepin Desktop Environment (DDE) File Manager.

Package: dfm-tools-gitk
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
  git,
  gitk
Description: Gitk context menu plugin for DDE File Manager
 Provides Gitk launcher context menu option for browsing Git repository history
 and branches in DDE File Manager.

Package: dfm-tools-git-cola
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
  git-cola
Description: Git Cola context menu plugin for DDE File Manager
 Provides Git Cola GUI integration context menu option for Git operations
 in DDE File Manager.

Package: dfm-tools-deb-builder
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
  dpkg-dev,
  debhelper
Description: DEB package builder context menu plugin for DDE File Manager
 Provides DEB package building tool context menu option for development
 directories in DDE File Manager.

Package: dfm-tools-deepin-project-downloader
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
  python3,
  git,
  python3-tk
Description: Deepin Project Downloader context menu plugin for DDE File Manager
 Provides Deepin project downloader tool context menu option for downloading
 and managing Deepin projects from various sources in DDE File Manager.

Package: dfm-tools-dde-dconfig-editor
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
  dde-dconfig-editor
Description: DDE DConfig Editor context menu plugin for DDE File Manager
 Provides DDE DConfig Editor launcher context menu option for managing system
 and application configurations in DDE File Manager.

Package: dfm-tools-changelog-update
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
  git,
  dpkg-dev
Description: ChangeLog upgrade context menu plugin for DDE File Manager
 Provides ChangeLog upgrade tool context menu option for automatically updating
 Debian changelog and version information in DDE File Manager.

Package: dfm-tools-d-feet
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
  d-feet
Description: D-Feet D-Bus debugger context menu plugin for DDE File Manager
 Provides D-Feet D-Bus debugger launcher context menu option for debugging
 D-Bus services in DDE File Manager.

Package: dfm-tools-vscode
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
  code
Description: Visual Studio Code context menu plugin for DDE File Manager
  Provides Visual Studio Code launcher context menu option for opening
  project directories in DDE File Manager.

Package: dfm-tools-qtcreator
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
  qtcreator,
  zenity | kdialog
Description: Qt Creator context menu plugin for DDE File Manager
 Provides Qt Creator launcher context menu option for opening Qt projects
 with automatic detection of qmake and CMake project types in DDE File Manager.

Package: dfm-tools-deb-saver
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
  python3,
  python3-tk
Description: DEB Package Saver context menu plugin for DDE File Manager
 Provides DEB Package Saver tool context menu option for downloading
 and managing DEB packages from various sources in DDE File Manager.

Package: dfm-tools-integration-all
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
  git,
  gitk,
  dpkg-dev,
  debhelper,
  python3,
  python3-tk,
  dde-dconfig-editor,
  d-feet,
  zenity | kdialog
Description: Integrated development tools menu plugin for DDE File Manager
 Provides a comprehensive integrated menu with all development tools including
 DEB builder, Gitk, Git Cola, Deepin Project Downloader, DDE DConfig Editor,
 ChangeLog Upgrade, D-Feet D-Bus debugger, Visual Studio Code, Qt Creator,
 and DEB Package Saver in DDE File Manager.